A web page for this utility can be found at:
    https://sg.danny.cz/scsi/lsscsi.html
or
  https://doug-gilbert.github.io/scsi/lsscsi.html

It includes many examples and a Download section.

To view the manpage in this directory (rather than the installed one, if
the package is installed) use:
    man ./lsscsi.8

Syntax checking
===============
Use:
    mandoc -W style lsscsi.8 > /dev/null
or
    mandoc -W style ls_name_value.8 > /dev/null
or
    mandoc -W style ls_name_value_rd.8 > /dev/null

The: 'cannot parse date, using it verbatim: TH February 2019' warning
is ignored.

Doug Gilbert
